videos.headline: Kansas QB Stanley slings TD to Luavasa
videos.description: Carter Stanley rips a pass over the middle to a wide-open Jack Luavasa for a 19-yard Kansas touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kansas QB Stanley slings TD to Luavasa) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Idrizi strolls into end zone for BC TD
videos.description: Boston College QB Anthony Brown finds Korab Idrizi all alone for a 20-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Idrizi strolls into end zone for BC TD) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kansas QB Stanley leapfrogs over defender
videos.description: Carter Stanley takes off for a 9-yard gain, but not before he hurdles over a Boston College defender.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kansas QB Stanley leapfrogs over defender) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: BC QB Brown catches TD on trick play
videos.description: Boston College runs a double reverse as CJ Lewis lofts a 12-yard touchdown to QB Anthony Brown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BC QB Brown catches TD on trick play) 2019/9/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams glides into end zone for Kansas TD
videos.description: Pooka Williams Jr. sees daylight en route to a 12-yard touchdown to extend Kansas' lead.
